{
  "stem": "1753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, in that small village, of course, they always-- the young kids that knew you were Jewish-- there were just a handful of Jews there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And perhaps between my brother and myself-- there may have been two, three other younger Jewish individuals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we were sort of a rarity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they-- they insulted us and called us names and reacted in an adverse way on our Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in that little village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later on, it intensified, even when I got to that other town, where there was a much larger Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as time progressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I felt it very-- as time went on, anyways, I got there in 1936.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was fair, the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, I was very young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I probably didn't understand what was going on around me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the anti-Semitism gradually increased.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from school in the winter, the regular school, to a regular public school, and got insulted, and beaten up, and--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you lousy Jew, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the teachers gradually became more and more anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you couldn't escape it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Initially, yeah, that was a public school, while simultaneously, twice a week, we also went to the-- to the Jewish schools, to like-- we didn't call it cheder, but you would call a cheder-- to learn Hebrew and Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, there was another Jewish family that I was assigned to them through the-- through a Jewish organization that helped Jewish families to get their-- themselves settled and maybe-- and incidentally, we were not that well off.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a relatively [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] not affluent family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, incidentally, my father already left Germany, he-- because of the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
